Hill:
Intermittent social runners
Benefit from targeted internal data and external data
In order to assess and enhance race performance in an engaging manner.

SubHill:
More perks/deals/discounts to RAM organized events are available to the runner as the runner participates in more RAM races.

Story:
As an intermittent social runner,
I want to earn credits/points after I participate in any RAM organized event/activity
So that I can receive specific monetary discounts

Acceptance Criteria:
Given I'm an intermittent social runner attended 3 races in last 3 month
When I go to RAM website after I checked out the third race
Then I got discount for next RAM race
